---+ Change password

---++ UKP domain

   * If you workstation is in the UKP domain, simply use the =passwd= command on the command line
   * Otherwise log in via ssh with your UKP identity to any compute server and use =passwd= on the command line there

---++ TK domain

   * Go to [[https://isman.tk.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de][ISMAN]]
   * Click on *Change Password*
   * Enter your account name, the old pasword and twice your new password

-- Main.RichardEckart - 2011-11-24